Ralcorp Rejects $4.9 Billion Conagra Bid, Adopts Shareholder Rights Plan

-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 
2011-05-04T18:07:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/ralcorp-rejects-4-9-billion-conagra-bid-adopts-shareholder-rights-plan.html
  Ralcorp Holdings Inc. (RAH)  said its board
of directors has unanimously determined that the unsolicited
non-binding proposal by  ConAgra Foods Inc. (CAG)  is not in the best
interests of shareholders.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  